Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,银河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危机，这下糟糕了\N紧张！紧张！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.65,0:00:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扑克光线  BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.72,0:00:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡闹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没关系，吃个饮茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着欢悦的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.66,0:00:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后一起向神明祈祷吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.07,0:00:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.50,0:00:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就让它顺其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.65,0:00:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有机关，没有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.12,0:00:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一掷的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无忧无虑的狂欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦想与希望的机关枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.73,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,锁定想要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧\NBRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人兴奋的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.50,0:01:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开辟天下无敌的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.69,0:01:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(游乐园名产，鸡肉薄荷蜜饯)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀呼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.73,0:01:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草\N这次的工作好好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.67,0:01:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，巡逻真的好好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.81,0:02:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...好好玩\N接下来巡逻哪个好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.38,0:02:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.22,0:02:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们这次的任务是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.32,0:02:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逮捕在咕咕嘟嘟乐园连续发生的\N儿童绑架未遂事件犯人，对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.34,0:02:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是从刚才看起来\N你好像只是在玩而已耶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才没有呢，我是在巡逻，巡逻啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇...是咕咕鸡耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看！如果是巡逻的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该要像那样\N保护离开父母身边的小孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.79,0:02:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保护小孩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保护小孩不受坏人威胁\N是我们的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此必须要时常有自制心\N谨慎行动才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且坏人也有很多种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.11,0:03:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们会找我们天使队来\N也是因为事先设想到这种状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而做出使自己的视野\N变狭窄的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在不太能说是上策吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是听不懂耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.55,0:03:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你听懂了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布偶装巡逻大作战？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近发生的多起绑架未遂事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主要集中发生在孩子们聚集的\N这个咕咕嘟嘟特区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.61,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，所以才请你们\N重点巡逻这个区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.25,0:03:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，可是这个广大的区域\N只靠笼统的巡逻是不够的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.39,0:03:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊是啊\N还有好多好玩的东西没玩到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.83,0:03:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽量把小孩集中在一个地方\N就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.20,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们穿上小孩最喜欢的吉祥物\N咕咕鸡的布偶装巡逻的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.44,0:04:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样小孩就会主动的靠过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.61,0:04:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且穿上布偶装\N还可以不让犯人发现地巡逻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.22,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好像很有趣，对吧香草？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此，这个方法不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个好方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么\N我们会尽快准备好布偶装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有两个咕咕鸡吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，还有一大堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我也要穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万万不可啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么能让薄荷．布拉曼修小姐\N做这种事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.91,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个咕咕嘟嘟行星\N是由布拉曼修集团经营的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们怎么可以这么失礼的\N让大小姐穿上布偶装呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不需要介意这些事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.63,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿上这个失礼的布偶装\N是我们这次的工作呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不能让您这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.83,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦您在这个能够掌控\N本乐园所有地方的房间监视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀呼，薄荷，你能看到我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...咕咕鸡！两只咕咕鸡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来跟咕咕鸡玩吧\N咕咕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个咕咕鸡，一动也不动喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！咕咕鸡死掉了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香...香草，怎么了？\N没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是祈祷的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此啊\N害我白担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大问题？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.66,0:05:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，布偶装作战计划有个大缺点\N那就是警戒范围会变得狭窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得这方法已经成功的\N把小孩集中起来了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个方法不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.74,0:05:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请好好想一想\N这里有这么多的设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.61,0:05:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说孩子们不全是为了\N和咕咕鸡玩才来这里的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.42,0:06:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家是不是都不太听父母的话\N那里玩玩，这里玩玩的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.96,0:06:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且稍微玩一下就会玩腻\N然后又去玩别的设施，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.76,0:06:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧\N所以在别的地方也要加强巡逻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.64,0:06:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在小孩很少去的闲静之处\N发生绑架的可能性非常的高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.48,0:06:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遗憾地\N我们必须个别行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.25,0:06:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来，例如...\N梅尔优去植物园，这样如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.65,0:06:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,植物阴暗处\N是最佳的犯罪地点，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.93,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且虽然说宇宙这么大\N但是适合穿花偶装的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想到梅尔优啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.37,0:06:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...是吗？真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.60,0:06:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来！大家来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.91,0:06:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家看，这个是食人花\N叶子的直径竟然有6公尺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是花很可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.12,0:07:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很适合花的装扮吧\N可爱吗？可爱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.09,0:07:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草则适合在\N最受欢迎的太空世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然得穿上有点\N不可思议的布偶装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是这样也蛮像\N香草的风格啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.03,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不太需要动\N在体力方面也比较轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然，还有广场也需要巡逻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.74,0:07:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就由剩下的我来穿\N咕咕鸡的布偶装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是怎么可以让大小姐穿布偶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.88,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说了\N你们好像忘了一件重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.85,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确，我是布拉曼修家的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.42,0:07:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，我也是天使队的一员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.53,0:07:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实之前在与此次类似的任务中\N我失去了我重要的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.47,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花．法兰波瓦兹\N以及...佛特．修特伦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.28,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天也是因为\N我是布拉曼修家的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没能被派往前线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是她们两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.59,0:08:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，只有她们两人\N没有对我特别看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对着沮丧的我投以热切微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝着枪林弹雨之中冲去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后两人并没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.54,0:08:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而她们两人的遗志\N仍然存活在我心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点，是绝不会消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.28,0:08:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使队的信条是\N所接受的工作一定贯彻到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是为了完成工作\N要我做什么我都会愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.36,0:08:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷．布拉曼修\N穿上咕咕鸡布偶装，前去巡逻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！那就麻烦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.05,0:09:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花样女孩\N好可爱的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.59,0:09:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面向我吧，梅尔优\N可是有点，可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了\N这种温暖、合身的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然我的眼光是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，犯人出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啦，放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我和香草正在追踪当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，犯人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，鸡在说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.19,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，薄荷\N你看，就是那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.56,0:10:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下\N站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下\N站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下\N站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下\N请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫你们站住没听到吗...\N这次的工作好好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们已经无路可逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是说要再继续玩官兵捉强盗呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对...对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.78,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了\N好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔？薄荷心情不错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.10,0:11:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前阵子抓到的绑架犯\N好像也偷了园区的布偶装呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.01,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然他们本人是否认了\N但是听说少了一只公鸡布偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕，好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下个菜单是天然梅尔优的视察勾芡\N不瞒你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是苹果蛋塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔，我肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.44,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是香甜好吃的果冻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇...看起来好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？等一下，不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.55,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...又甜又好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,满天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.64,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我新月的曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.54,0:12:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作了梦之后，变得想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侧耳倾听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.59,0:12:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是听见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.36,0:12:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人兴奋的天线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.37,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要让它睡着  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.37,0:13:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,处女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.44,0:13:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向魔羯座的你发出\N急电，急电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.55,0:13:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘着飞马的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
